data.description: Discover the perfect blend of elegance and modernity in this exquisite 4 beds, 2.5 bath home in the desirable Campus Highlands neighborhood. Recently renovated, this home boasts an open floor plan with vaulted ceilings and a grand staircase, creating a spacious and inviting atmosphere. Gleaming hardwood floors lead you to the stunning, newly upgraded kitchen, complete with quartz countertops, a stylish backsplash, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. Cozy up by the wood fireplace in the family room, showcasing custom tile work, offering a perfect spot for relaxation. With a 3 car garage and a shed.  Relax on the deck in the fully fenced backyard w/fruit trees. Great location!
